    {
      "text": "A reskinned version of Super Solitaire for the Japanese market. Instead of a standard menu featuring the 12 Solitaire varieties, this release frames those same modes around an island with each mode corresponding with a location. Instead of digitized photos and landscapes, the backgrounds of each mode are replaced with anime girls.",
